{"tid":1682664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港知專學院學⽣聲明】","createTime":"2019-10-30T07:45:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T15:28:37.000Z","uid":210246,"like":441,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":119,"replies":[{"pid":"003d137d79066d3bf5175a7d29eae24553a4ad9b","tid":1682664,"uid":210246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T07:45:42.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">【香港知專學院學⽣聲明】 </div><br />\n\r<br />\n香港知專學院副院長⿈偉祖於昨⽇（10⽉29⽇）答應學⽣會於本⽇下午⼀時半會在同⼀地點與同學⾒⾯及即時處理、聯絡有關部⾨能否公開其他CCTV⽚段。但在本⽇早上⼗⼀時，在同學們仍在校園上課的時候，校⽅發出電郵指校院需要進⾏緊急維修⼯程，未能進⾏和平有效的溝通。在本⽇下午⼀時三⼗分，校⽅未有派出任何⼈員向學⽣及在場傳媒交代有關事宜。 <br />\n\r<br />\n香港知專學院學⽣表示對事件感到非常失望及遺憾，校⽅出爾反爾，副院長昨⽇答應學⽣的承諾亦灰⾶煙滅，校⽅只是利⽤電郵作出不清晰的「回應」，⽽在場的校⽅保安對本⽇的安排表示完全不知情。同學們在現場等待校⽅多時，卻連⼀句「不會到場」的答覆也沒有。 <br />\r\n雙⽅在昨⽇苦苦商討的成果被校⽅完全毀滅，同時，同學們對於學校的信⼼亦已消失。 <br />\n\r<br />\n香港知專學院學⽣ <br />\r\n2019年10⽉30⽇"},{"pid":"1798f96e670c02eb7a82d6d797f7bb1ef150305f","tid":1682664,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T07:46:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ercBKS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ercBKS</a><br />\n【TVB 嚇到瀨事，事實證明，洗版真係work】今日洗版任務 - 田原香"},{"pid":"8e8b22acfd6b3733645ee538b8ba631c94e38230","tid":1682664,"uid":157069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T07:46:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b913cddf571bafce5668dd8ce54cf3557fc4dd7","tid":1682664,"uid":333631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T07:46:35.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f76c16aea87028580ddc0cb8ddc1e2cfbd1299fe","tid":1682664,"uid":149041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T07:46:36.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"5152be7dc8783f2d7b1edc142669d37230d400a4","tid":1682664,"uid":157069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T07:46:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\